<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Learn more about our company and our values</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>We indeed take great pleasure to introduce ourselves as specialized Contractors in the field of mechanical engineering construction. We are having more than 30 years of experience in the field of Fabrication and Erection of Steel structure, piping, Tank fabrication & various type of Engineering construction work.</p>
                
                <p>We are equipped with full-fledged contract division comprising highly skilled and technically well advanced work crew that has years of experience dealing with constantly changing technical know-how in the field of various types Mechanics Engineering works.</p>
                
                <h3>Our Group Companies</h3>
                <div class="group-companies">
                    <div class="company">
                        <h4>Romecca HP Coats</h4>
                        <p>One of the Group organisation in the field of high performing protective coating, have been undertaking and executing various kind of specialized industrial coating for leading Indian and MNC organizations. A span of more than 30 years of experience in the field Industrial Coating.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="company">
                        <h4>Vimala Group of Companies</h4>
                        <p>Also our group company looking after the heavy mechanical engineering works, have undertaken and successfully completed many major and prestigious projects like Nuclear and thermal power plants, oil refinery, steel plants, food processing unit, chemical plants etc.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="about-image">
                <img src="" alt="Our Company">
            </div> -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Leadership</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="team-photo">
                        <img src="\image\pps1.jpg" alt="Founder Photo">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Prem Kumar Sah</h3>
                    <h2>(Gupta Ji)</h2>

                    <p class="designation">Founder & Visionary Leader</p>
                    <p class="location">Based in Bachau, Gujrat,India</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="team-photo">
                        <img src="\image\mk1.jpg" alt="Managing Officer Photo">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Mithilesh Kumar</h3>
                    <p class="designation">Managing Director & CEO</p>
                    <p class="location">Based in Bachau, Gujrat,India</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="team-description">Our leadership comprises visionary individuals with decades of industry experience and a proven track record of success. They combine strategic thinking with hands-on expertise to guide our organization towards excellence.</p>
            <p>The founder's pioneering vision and the managing officer's operational excellence create a powerful synergy that drives our company forward. Their leadership ensures we remain at the forefront of innovation while maintaining our core values.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Safety First</h3>
                    <p>Safety is our primary concern. We guide all the working items and the supervisors on all safety aspects.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <h3>Quality Control</h3>
                    <p>The management team analyses all on-going and past projects to device systems to improve quality.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i>
                    <h3>Project Planning</h3>
                    <p>The project management team works on the time schedules, procurement schedules and the manpower needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
